# ── Metadata Source ─────────────────────────────────────────
# You need at least ONE of these API keys for the app to work.

# TMDB API Key (recommended — full features)
# Get yours at: https://www.themoviedb.org/settings/api
# Enables: trending, popular, genre discovery, TV data, cast photos, trailers
VITE_TMDB_API_KEY=

# OMDB API Key (temporary fallback while TMDB account is verified)
# Get yours at: https://www.omdbapi.com/apikey.aspx
# Limited to: search + details only (no trending, genre discovery, TV show data)
# Set this in the app Settings page (not as an env var)
